Get,Exchange,Rates,provides,free,exchange,rates,for,nearly,every,currency,in,the,world,The,API,lets,developers,access,exchange,rate,information,both,current,and,historical,and,integrate,it,into,their,systems,Rates,for,all,currencies,are,updated,every,two,minutes,The,simple,API,uses,a,RESTful,call,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON